      <title>米其林挑战欧盟寻找轮胎卡特尔证据</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-17/michelin-challenges-eu-s-hunt-for-evidence-of-tire-cartel</link>
      <description><![CDATA[随着监管机构席卷整个轮胎行业，寻找涉嫌垄断价格卡特尔的证据，米其林正在挑战欧盟对其设施进行反垄断搜查的合法性。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-17/michelin-challenges-eu-s-hunt-for-evidence-of-tire-cartel</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 17 Apr 2024 09:03:13 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>黄金价格保持在接近纪录水平，交易者不考虑以后降息的可能性</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-17/gold-xauusd-holds-near-record-as-traders-overlook-delayed-cuts-scenario</link>
      <description><![CDATA[尽管投资者权衡美联储主席杰罗姆·鲍威尔的信息转变，金价仍稳定在历史高位附近，鲍威尔表示美联储维持利率不变的时间可能会比原计划更长。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-17/gold-xauusd-holds-near-record-as-traders-overlook-delayed-cuts-scenario</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 17 Apr 2024 00:35:21 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>由于伊朗风险加剧，油价在美国库存数据公布前小幅下跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-16/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-april-17</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于市场持续关注以色列对伊朗周末袭击的反应以及美国原油库存可能增加，油价小幅走低。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-16/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-april-17</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 16 Apr 2024 23:21:40 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>展望缓解对波音交付的担忧，联合航空股价上涨</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-16/united-airlines-cuts-2024-aircraft-plan-amid-growth-challenges</link>
      <description><![CDATA[联合航空控股公司(United Airlines Holdings Inc.)预计本季度利润好于预期，该公司股价上涨，缓解了人们对波音公司飞机延误和监管压力将使扩张计划面临风险的担忧。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-16/united-airlines-cuts-2024-aircraft-plan-amid-growth-challenges</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 16 Apr 2024 20:10:05 GMT</pubDate>
